06:50.390 --> 06:51.721
<i>It's Jason.</i>

06:51.723 --> 06:54.758
<i>I haven't heard from him
since yesterday morning.</i>

06:54.760 --> 06:56.827
<i>I thought he wasn't texting
back because he was busy,</i>

06:56.829 --> 06:59.463
<i>but then I called him when he was
supposed to be getting off work</i>

06:59.465 --> 07:01.499
<i>and he didn't answer.</i>

07:01.501 --> 07:02.565
<i>I don't know.</i>

07:02.567 --> 07:03.968
<i>Maybe it's nothing,</i>

07:03.970 --> 07:06.237
