07:44.977 --> 07:46.478
Only if she asks.

07:46.480 --> 07:48.547
<i>Could you try
to call him for me</i>

07:48.549 --> 07:50.948
<i>and then let me know
if he's okay?</i>

07:50.950 --> 07:51.849
<i>I just need to know.</i>

07:51.851 --> 07:54.220
Yeah, I'll try... for you.

07:55.522 --> 07:57.154
I doubt he's gonna pick up
my phone call,

07:57.156 --> 07:59.558
