go straight to his place.

07:59.560 --> 08:02.626
<i>Thank you so much.</i>

08:02.628 --> 08:04.498
<i>You're a really great guy.</i>

08:06.833 --> 08:08.032
Jason!

08:11.505 --> 08:12.672
You in there?

08:18.711 --> 08:19.710
