when she calls.

08:24.717 --> 08:27.152
All right.
I won't tell you.

08:51.945 --> 08:53.845
- Is it another girl?
- Don't worry about it.

08:53.847 --> 08:56.748
- Is it another girl?
- I thought you didn't wanna know any details.

08:56.750 --> 08:58.550
You're right.
I don't.

08:58.552 --> 09:00.020
Fuck me.

09:21.842 --> 09:23.609
<i>Hello?</i>

09:23.611 --> 09:25.411
Hi. Is this Emilia?

09:25.413 --> 09:26.878
<i>Who is this?</i>

09:26.880 --> 09:28.648
My name's Roy. I think you
might know my friend Jason?

09:28.650 --> 09:30.416
<i>Jason...?</i>

09:30.418 --> 09:31.683
Jason Lowe.

09:31.685 --> 09:33.486
I'm at his apartment right now,
and I...

09:33.488 --> 09:35.555
