on a napkin.

09:35.557 --> 09:38.424
<i>Oh, that Jason.</i>

09:38.426 --> 09:40.725
<i>Uh, we were supposed to go
on a date the other day,</i>

09:40.727 --> 09:42.861
<i>but he blew me off.</i>

09:42.863 --> 09:44.029
I'm sorry he blew you off.

09:44.031 --> 09:46.031
