looking forward to it.

09:46.033 --> 09:48.800
<i>I figured I would
try to get to know him.</i>

09:48.802 --> 09:50.802
<i>Thought he was kinda cute.</i>

09:50.804 --> 09:54.773
<i>Can't say I'm surprised to
find out he's just another...</i>

09:54.775 --> 09:56.975
<i>...butthead.</i>

09:56.977 --> 09:58.313
<i>Are you laughing at me?</i>

09:59.547 --> 10:02.381
