term since the seventh grade.

10:02.383 --> 10:05.184
<i>I like it.
It's fitting.</i>

10:05.186 --> 10:07.088
<i>What was your name again?</i>

10:08.623 --> 10:11.424
- Roy.
- <i>Roy.</i>

10:11.426 --> 10:13.593
Listen, I know
this is a long shot,

10:13.595 --> 10:14.594
um,

10:14.596 --> 10:16.229
but would you happen to know
where Jason is?

10:16.231 --> 10:18.830
<i>I haven't heard from him.</i>

10:18.832 --> 10:21.534
<i>I wish I had,
I could have helped.</i>

10:21.536 --> 10:22.501
<i>But...</i>

10:22.503 --> 10:24.337
Well, um...

10:24.339 --> 10:25.671
...Thanks, anyway.

10:25.673 --> 10:26.939
It was nice talking to you.

10:26.941 --> 10:29.108
<i>It was nice
talking to you, too, Roy.</i>

10:29.110 --> 10:31.644
