be up this late.</i>

10:31.646 --> 10:33.615
<i>It's way past my bedtime.</i>

10:34.449 --> 10:35.848
Good night, Emilia.

10:35.850 --> 10:37.385
<i>Good night, Roy.</i>

10:47.028 --> 10:49.395
Nothing's out of place.
His computer was still there.

10:49.397 --> 10:51.030
