my Christmas shopping.

11:29.505 --> 11:30.269
Oh, yeah?

11:30.271 --> 11:32.406
You're going to love your gift.

11:32.408 --> 11:33.839
You got me a present?

11:33.841 --> 11:35.676
It's nothing really.

11:35.678 --> 11:37.045
That's sweet.

11:40.081 --> 11:42.251
What did you two argue about?

11:45.554 --> 11:47.423
You don't have to answer that.

11:50.058 --> 11:51.891
Thanks for talking to me.

11:51.893 --> 11:53.295
You don't have to thank me.

12:01.370 --> 12:02.404
Kate?

12:03.272 --> 12:04.807
