12:52.822 --> 12:54.256
Call me if you hear from Jason.

12:57.560 --> 12:58.762
Fuck.

13:02.364 --> 13:04.333
Samantha?
It's Roy.

13:05.167 --> 13:06.868
I feel really bad
about last night.

13:06.870 --> 13:09.336
