I wanted to ask...

13:09.338 --> 13:10.540
Do you wanna go to lunch?

13:22.585 --> 13:24.852
Okay, I know
that you're in there.

13:24.854 --> 13:27.490
I just saw that guy leave.

13:29.459 --> 13:30.858
