14:57.213 --> 14:59.113
um...

14:59.115 --> 15:02.216
I feel really bad
about my friend standing you up.

15:02.218 --> 15:07.088
Would you-would you want to have
a do-over with me instead?

15:07.090 --> 15:09.259
