I won't do the same.

15:13.297 --> 15:15.131
<i>What did you have in mind?</i>

15:18.502 --> 15:19.904
Uh...

15:26.710 --> 15:29.011
Are you Roy?

15:29.013 --> 15:30.714
You must be Emilia.

15:31.615 --> 15:34.650
Good call on the sweater.

15:34.652 --> 15:36.585
I figured if you
didn't like the look of me

15:36.587 --> 15:37.886
you could just
pretend you were alone

15:37.888 --> 15:39.621
and never have to speak to me.

15:39.623 --> 15:42.126
Why wouldn't
I like the look of you?

15:43.193 --> 15:44.762
We've never met 'til now.

15:45.663 --> 15:47.364
I like the way you look.

15:47.965 --> 15:50.599
You look... fun.

15:53.004 --> 15:54.138
I'll take that.

15:55.072 --> 15:58.240
No, I live with
my brother, actually.

15:58.242 --> 16:01.076
We inhabited the house
after my parents died.

16:01.078 --> 16:03.679
Do you mean "inherited"?

16:03.681 --> 16:04.948
Probably.

16:04.950 --> 16:07.349
I-I get that one wrong.

16:07.351 --> 16:09.418
You probably inhabited it, too.

16:09.420 --> 16:12.055
Don't worry.
The other day I said "appetizer"

16:12.057 --> 16:13.890
instead of "appraisal."

16:13.892 --> 16:16.694
That customer was very confused.

16:18.395 --> 16:19.330
Thanks.

16:20.197 --> 16:22.230
Sorry to hear
about your parents.

16:22.232 --> 16:25.367
They must have been young. How
old were you when they passed?

16:25.369 --> 16:28.236
