16:28.238 --> 16:29.808
Six years old.

16:31.943 --> 16:34.644
That's horrible. We don't
have to talk about this.

16:34.646 --> 16:36.313
Okay.

16:38.016 --> 16:40.484
What's your favorite part
about Christmas?

16:41.385 --> 16:43.586
I like spending time
with my family...

16:43.588 --> 16:46.055
I mean, it's the only time
of year I get to see my parents.

16:46.057 --> 16:47.322
People I don't
get to see very often.

16:47.324 --> 16:49.060
I just like the togetherness.

16:49.961 --> 16:51.728
