for dinner tonight.

18:02.400 --> 18:03.801
Tonight?

18:03.803 --> 18:06.138
Yeah. 6:30.

18:07.305 --> 18:09.139
Well, I guess I don't
have anything going on today.

18:09.141 --> 18:12.076
I can call you later
with the address.

18:12.078 --> 18:14.379
Okay, that sounds great.

18:15.681 --> 18:18.148
- I'll see you tonight!
- Okay.

18:18.150 --> 18:19.484
