for a couple minutes.

18:32.531 --> 18:34.098
Better make it fast.

18:34.100 --> 18:35.666
I don't wanna wait
in the car too long.

18:35.668 --> 18:37.603
I'll go as fast as I can.
I promise.

18:41.306 --> 18:43.042
Did you like him?

18:44.110 --> 18:45.175
Yeah.

18:45.177 --> 18:48.712
Well, maybe next year,
if you still like him,

18:48.714 --> 18:49.882
